1986;;Monster in the Closet;;American;;Bob Dahlin;;Paul Dooley, Claude Akins, Stella Stevens, Howard Duff, Frank Ashmore;;comedy horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monster_in_the_Closet;;After a series of murders in San Francisco that all take place inside closets, a reporter and his scientist friend decide to uncover the mystery and save California.[3]